Feature: Add new Product

Background:
Given Add new product using Service class

Scenario: Adding a new product all valid details
When All product details provided are valid
| Iphone 15 pro  |
| 256gb, Deep Purple |
| 149990.00 |
Then return the product saved

Scenario: Adding a new product with name as null
When Provided null to any parameter
| null |
| 256gb, Deep Purple |
| 149990.00 |
Then Throw invalid name exception

Scenario: Adding a new product with null description
When Provided null to any parameter
| Iphone 15 pro |
| null |
| 149990.00 |
Then Throw invalid description exception

Scenario: Adding a new product with null price
When Provided null to any parameter
| Iphone 15 pro |
| 256gb, Deep Purple |
| null |
Then Throw invalid price exception